arts.ttl: Haraldsson's strike fends off Sturm Graz comeback in Lille
arts.sum: Hakon Arnar Haraldsson's strike, a minute after coming off the bench, helps Lille see off Sturm Graz 3-2 despite the away side coming back from 2-0 down to level the game on matchday six of the Champions League group phase.
